fields.name: Excalibur
fields.description: The legendary Sword of the Lake

fields.name: Acrobatics
fields.description: Acrobatics determines how well your character can move about, keep his balance or jump and land softly.

fields.name: Acting
fields.description: Acting determines your ability to tell convincing lies and to, in a convincing way, play a role.  The skill is used to deceive others, but also by religious characters when they participate in High Festivals in temples.

fields.name: Alarm Bell
fields.description: An alarm bell that only the spell-caster can hear will ring and ward him if certain conditions are present in an alarm zone.  The alarm zone is an area up to 20' radius large.  The spell-caster can himself define what shall trigger the alarm bell.  if can be if a certain creature enters, or if a certain number of gold nuggets are present, if the temperature drops below 0, or whatever.  The imagine of the player is the only limit.  A character entering an alarm zone can test his Rune Lore against a DD equal to 15 to understand that he has entered some sort of sorcerous zone.

fields.name: Ice Heart
fields.description: Cast upon a swords & daggers weapon or an arrowhead (and for Sorcerers a bolt-head or a spear weapon as well).  The weapon inflicts D8 (PL 3), D10 (PL 4), or D12 (PL 5) extra Cold Damage to a target if the attacker achieves at least a Near Miss.

fields.name: Purify Nutrition
fields.description: 2 day rations of drink and food * spell PL is purified of all poisons.

fields.name: Remove Curse
fields.description: Removes a curse.  To remove the curse, the spell-caster tests his spell proficiency of the spell-caster who cursed the cursed individual / object.

fields.name: Remove Paralysis
fields.description: Removes paralysis from one individual.  To succeed doing this the spell-caster needs to test his spell proficiency against a DD equal to 9 + the spell proficiency of the spell-caster who paralysed the paralysed individual/object.

fields.name: Resist Disease
fields.description: An individual is given increased Disease Resistance equal to the spell-caster's spell proficiency.  This spell does not help already diseased individuals.

fields.name: Resist Poison
fields.description: An individual is given increased Poison Resistance equal to the spell-caster's spell proficiency.  This spell does not help already poisoned individuals.

fields.name: Restoration
fields.description: Restores all damaged character attributes in an individual (PL 1).  If the damage is defined as irreparable the damaged attributes can be restored anyhow if the spell is cast with PL 10.

fields.name: Reverse Petrification
fields.description: A petrified individual can be turned back into original form.  The spell-caster must test his spell proficiency against a DD equal to 12 + the spell proficiency of the petrifier.

fields.name: Sanctuary
fields.description: A sanctuary up to 50' radius is created.

fields.name: Sacred Ground
fields.description: An area up to 50' radius large is turned in a sacred ground.

fields.name: Seven-Mile-Boots
fields.description: The target of this spell can add the spell PL * 5' to his Tempo skill (but not in relation to climbing, crawling, sneaking and tracking) and also jump twice as long and high.

fields.name: Silence
fields.description: No sound can escape from a 20' radius large zone, centered on an object or individual.

fields.name: Snowflake
fields.description: An object or individual falls like a snowflake to the ground.

fields.name: Sorcerous Shape
fields.description: The spell-caster can create a hamr of any animal skin he may come across.

fields.name: Sorcerous Sleep
fields.description: One individual falls asleep, and can not be awoken by normal means.

fields.name: Spirit Voice
fields.description: A voice can be heard from somewhere when certain conditions are met.

fields.name: Summon Creature
fields.description: A creature is summoned to serve the spell-caster.

fields.name: Telekinesis
fields.description: An individual or object weighing up to 255 lbs can be lifted and moved about with a speed of 1' per second.

fields.name: Telepathy
fields.description: The spell-caster can communicate with another human being from a distance, even if the other individual is sleeping.

fields.name: Teleportation
fields.description: An object or individual touched is teleported to a location up to 1000' away and in sight of the spell-caster.

fields.name: Totem Animal
fields.description: The spell-caster is not affected by fear, he will bot be stunned and not be knocked unconscious

fields.name: Trojan Fortress
fields.description: The target is teleported into a maze in a spirit world.

fields.name: Veil
fields.description: The spell makes it harder to see the target.  Spell-caster or target gets the spell caster's spell proficiency / 3 (rounded up) as a mod to Stealth tests and DV.

fields.name: Void Travel
fields.description: Stop time for all others but the spell caster

fields.name: Wall of Thorns
fields.description: A 5' thick wall of thorns with a width of 10' and a height of up to 20' grows up from the ground during the night where the spell-caster wants it to.

fields.name: Whirlwind
fields.description: A whirlwind under the spell-caster's control appears.

fields.name: Wind Gust
fields.description: One creature with size ≤ the spells PL is pushed out of balance and falls.
